ArnoldXGen Op
======================

The ArnoldXGen Op is used to create a volume location with appropriate
Arnold procedural plugin DSO arguments set up and ready to go.

Environment Variables
---------------------

KATANA_HOME  The Katana installation directory at compile-time

Building
--------

1. Ensure the environment variables listed above have been set.
2. Run 'make'.
3. Run 'make install'.
